1936;;When Knights Were Bold;;British;;Jack Raymond;;Jack Buchanan, Fay Wray;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/When_Knights_Were_Bold_(1936_film);;Sir Guy de Vere inherits his father's estate while serving with the British army in India. He returns home to take up his new role, but is greeted with hostility by his family and servants. After a drunken evening, a bump on the head with a suit of armour sends Sir Guy back to the 1400s and the golden age of chivalry.